        <Paragraphs>
          <Paragraph>
            <TextRuns>
              <TextRun>
                <Value>Dear Valued Customer:

We appreciate your business. Do not pay. Your bank account will be electronically debited for the above charges. Please ensure that our records reflect the correct banking information for this account to avoid any unnecessary NSF penalties. If you have any questions about your account or need to make any changes or updates, please contact your account representative at 888-851-7558.</Value>
                <Style>
                  <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                </Style>
              </TextRun>
            </TextRuns>
            <Style>
              <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
            </Style>
          </Paragraph>
        </Paragraphs>
        <Top>3.7in</Top>
        <Left>0.1in</Left>
        <Height>0.8in</Height>
        <Width>6.5in</Width>
